commit.message: Add python_requires header
Prepare CHANGELOG for 1.0.0 release
Fix classfiers for 1.0 release

Due to the live_server_scope option, require pytest>=5.2

The fixture uses the dynamic fixture support introduced in pytest 5.2:

https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/blob/master/doc/en/changelog.rst#pytest-520-2019-09-28

Change --live-server-scope to an ini option

This was brought up in #113, but was missed.

Change scope of live server to session (#113)

live_server fixture scope can be configured, defaults to session

Fixes #62, Fixes #112, Closes #63 

Co-authored-by: Brian Cherinka <havok2063@hotmail.com>
